body:
This is my first mod. Made with MCreator.

A forge vanilla-friendly mod that adds bronze armor and tools.
The current version is for 1.20.1.

Made a fabric version, you can find it in the files.

Current content:
- Bronze Armor (stronger than chainmail, weaker than iron);
- Bronze tools (less durability than iron tools but slightly faster);
- Bronze nugget, ingot and block;
- Bronze Mixture (slightly faster smelting speed) and block of raw bronze;
- Raw tin and raw tin block (the block has a chance to generate naturally); 
- Tin ore (drops between 1 and 3 pieces of raw tin, generates between 0 and 175), nugget, ingot, block; 
- Tin knife (low damage, high attack speed);

Compatible with my other mod:
- More Vanilla Tools: unlocks bronze recipes for the extra tools,

Check the images for more information.

Feel free to use it on your modpack, just make sure to credit it and don't claim it as your own.
Have fun!
